Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,(最近我老婆沉迷於這種東西)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,(Madonna出品)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好美味的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的老婆\N婚後一直很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也有煩惱的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老婆很容易沉迷一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這次又沉迷什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最近迷上了保齡球買的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我在電視上看到我覺得好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣還可以打掃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這個很寬鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,還不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要是肚子餓了就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我來修理空調的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是預約的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,從上周吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:05:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不用空調嗎\N冰箱還在用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看\N拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要去工作了嗎\N因為要趕工期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾也出去玩一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,下周出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我對妳一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啊
